  "description": "Adds more Structures to Minecraft with 4 new Bossfights!",
  "body": "<h1 id=\"hello-and-welcome\">Hello and Welcome to Bloxy's Structures!</h1>\n<h4>This mod adds an all-new dimension called The Adventure Realm.<br>In the dimension you will find new Structures, new bosses, and enemies to face, but of course.<br>If you succeed you get all new items and tools to help you on your journey!</h4>\n<p>Check out the Images to see how some of the Structures and the Dimension look - <em>(Mod version 1.15 and above)</em><br>If you're curious, the shaders are called \"Complementary Unbound\"</p>\n\n## \n<details>\n<summary>Videos</summary>\n\n<p><span class=\"mce-preview-object mce-object-iframe\" contenteditable=\"false\" data-mce-object=\"iframe\" data-mce-p-allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-p-src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/F71A4cp9Rrg\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/F71A4cp9Rrg\" width=\"560\" height=\"314\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/F71A4cp9Rrg\"></iframe><span class=\"mce-shim\"></span></span><br><span contenteditable=\"false\" data-mce-object=\"iframe\" class=\"mce-preview-object mce-object-iframe\" data-mce-p-allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-p-src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/YxbXoxsU3Yc\"><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"314\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/YxbXoxsU3Yc\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe><span class=\"mce-shim\"></span></span><br><span contenteditable=\"false\" data-mce-object=\"iframe\" class=\"mce-preview-object mce-object-iframe\" data-mce-p-allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-p-src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/syjBaUHcD0w\"><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"314\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/syjBaUHcD0w\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe><span class=\"mce-shim\"></span></span><br><span contenteditable=\"false\" data-mce-object=\"iframe\" class=\"mce-preview-object mce-object-iframe\" data-mce-p-allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-p-src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/7OcNTVK_oIg\"><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"314\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/7OcNTVK_oIg\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe><span class=\"mce-shim\"></span></span><span contenteditable=\"false\" data-mce-object=\"iframe\" class=\"mce-preview-object mce-object-iframe\" data-mce-p-allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-p-src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WlVxQsOoFTc\"><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"314\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WlVxQsOoFTc\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe><span class=\"mce-shim\"></span></span></p>\n\n</details>\n\n## \n\n<p><strong>- Other Details -<br></strong>The mod can be put on any modpack, both for personal and commercial use.<br>The mod is made with MCreator and Blockbench.</p>\n\n\n",
